text: Hey Muniza! I've added a few notes onto you animation, I think it has a lot of potential in there. Only a few notes in there. I really like how you've pushed her expressions. Overall I'd say that as it's quite big movements, keep it simple then you'll be able to read it easy :slightly_smiling_face:
Thank you for your crit! I'll make a start on those changes tonight :sparkles:
My friend/housemate Kirstie went to the QVFX event last week and said she met you! I had no idea that you worked for them - I'll have to attend a QVFX event soon :smile:
